spec_data.Name: perl-Authen-SASL-SASLprep
spec_data.Description:
This Perl module implements the SASLprep specification, which describes how to
prepare Unicode strings representing user names and passwords for comparison.
SASLprep is a profile of the stringprep algorithm.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 07:16:30 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Stringprep profile for user names and passwords (RFC 4013)
